* List registered runners missing a bib number
* Purpose:          Identifies registered runners who have not yet been assigned a bib.
* When to use:      Pre-race setup, packet pickup, or right before the start.
* Output1:          Displays the list in the browser.
* Output2:          Saves the list to "c:\tmp\runners_missing_bib.txt" (open with a text editor).

Select              Bib
EQ                  

Destination         Browser
*Destination        %temp_dir%\runners_missing_bib.txt